{"tid":2509079,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建制派：審計報告是中央平衡各勢力的一種默契 入境處公開指責食相難看","createTime":"2021-04-29T07:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T11:28:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"149549c71ad24a8c11c6526e4dc128ac2f3fd53c","tid":2509079,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊稱入境處發聲明回應審計報告做法罕見<br />\n<br />\n立法會政府帳目委員會副主席謝偉俊說，入境處昨晚發聲明回應新一份審計報告的做法較為罕見。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊說，根據相關機制，政府部門、審計署及帳委會有共識，在帳委會正式聆訊前，各方都不就報告作公開辯論及評論，過往因應傳媒關注，個別部門都會在聆訊前對報告作回應，但部門自己發新聞稿或聲明，可說是比較罕見。<br />\n<br />\n至於會否影響帳委會日後聆訊，謝偉俊相信影響不大，帳委會亦會持平處理，包括聽取各方說法後再作判斷。他又表示，現階段不想就事件作回應，稍後帳委會將再召開閉門會議討論有關事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588397-20210429.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588397-20210429.htm&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwc5qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=7d90126a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588397-20210429.htm&h=7cd444c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588397-20210429.htm</a>"},{"pid":"801371ea3522c58127294ea4805627e158d3f3e9","tid":2509079,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊黃架"},{"pid":"1391818d91c6eb97dbe8ec001f3d3dddcb7e77b2","tid":2509079,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671f28b18ddbe18f5de66ec173fad42fc89e4259","tid":2509079,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"又扮反對派"},{"pid":"7e1404500e11db97c537f602c028a1f6a6c21e70","tid":2509079,"uid":224066,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17155801/875.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F17155801%2F875.png&h=25bc6fa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d48c5a84ce0fe84a04419178c3686fa139fcdd1","tid":2509079,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"傻仔仲唔識死。人哋話到明你唔係佢嗰瓣，就唔好喺度呀芝呀佐。你估佢會怕你個仲係由廢物組成嘅委員會咩。不過，以底褲超人嘅有限智慧，我估都仲識得喺最後關頭下跪嘅。"},{"pid":"0fdfe907289c168956143fa8d6790fa4d2e9ea86","tid":2509079,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:42:24.000Z","msg":"曱甴部順便接管埋海關嚟做"},{"pid":"cd09485307e98c1b70b108afd61e00c2a5f58b85","tid":2509079,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"軍政府喎家陣"}]}